    "title": "Walk-in Drive Category Manager at Park Avenue",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Category Manager with drive and ambition, Park Avenue in Gurgaon is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Park Avenue:\nPark Avenue is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Park Avenue!",
